✔️Childhood dream fulfilled. I’ve always dreamed of having a really nice NBA regulation sized basketball hoop at home. Most of my childhood, all the way through high school, was spent playing basketball for school and Summer leagues. This month, that decades long dream became a reality. 🙏 Huge thanks to @dominatorsports for making a badass all aluminum and tempered glass hoop that can withstand the wet and soggy PNW. I am so happy. Now it’s time to get my daughter to the WNBA. LFG!!!! 
.
